Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:41.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,ProSeka AfterTalk: Reaching Out for a Tangled Tomorrow, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:48.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm Hinata Sato, the voice of Mizuki Akiyama from Nightcord at 25:00.
Comment: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Fan Letter Corner ===
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:55.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,This ProSeka AfterTalk is a stream where we look back on the event while reading the messages you've sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,This time, we're focusing on the "Reaching Out for a Tangled Tomorrow" event.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:03.18,Default,host,0,0,0,,I hope you all enjoyed the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:07.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,The event actually just ended yesterday. How was it for all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,Did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really hope you all had a good time with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:18.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,It was a story about the members of Niigo facing their own futures
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:21.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,and thinking about what they want to do later in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:32.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,I think it might have really hit home for those of you who are at that stage of deciding on your education or career path.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:42.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,Starting in April, AfterTalk got a bit of a renewal, and we've been collecting messages in advance via the official ProSeka Discord and email.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:44.98,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much to everyone who sent one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:50.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll be reading some of your messages during the show, so look forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:59.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,Also, if you want to share your thoughts on the event or this stream, please post using the hashtag #ProSekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:04.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm keeping an eye on the YouTube chat, and I'll check the hashtag later too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:07.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,so I'll try to pick out any comments that catch my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:19.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,There are so many overseas comments! I can barely find the Japanese ones. People are saying the ribbon is cute, or that my hair matches Mizuki's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:24.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,The stream is probably a bit delayed, so people are just now noticing my hair and outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:30.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,I always try to do this, but I really made an effort to match the event illustration today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:32.41,Default,host,0,0,0,,I came here with the illustration in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:33.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,Good evening, and thank you all for joining.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:37.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,Oh, someone said, "The story and the new song were so good, I sobbed."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll talk more about the song in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:43.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,When I saw it at home, I was like, "What is this?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,I mean, "What even is this?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:48.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really felt the incredible effort the team put into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:50.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:53.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll save that talk for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:12:00.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,Now then, let's dive right into the story for "Reaching Out for a Tangled Tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:04.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,We've received messages about this story as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:07.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,so I'd like to look back on the plot while reading through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:11.28,Default,host_meta,0,0,0,,First, we have a message from Kotori no Mama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.56,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Hello, Hina-san! Konnigo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,Konnigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:16.10,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"My child and I both enjoy playing ProSeka together."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:19.92,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The event featuring my favorite, Mizuki-chan, was incredibly cute, funny, and moving."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:28.04,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm so glad we got to see Mizuki-chan's various feelings through her past experiences and her interactions with those around her."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:36.50,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I think it's very difficult to stay true to yourself and keep doing what you love without getting lost or hitting a wall."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:41.72,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"But I believe that if you hold onto those feelings, the day will come when they are rewarded."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:48.20,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Just like the members of Niigo, I'm sure there are people out there who will see you for who you are"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.00,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and accept you."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:52.50,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I truly love the stories in ProSeka."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:55.78,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Hina-san, thank you so much for always voicing her."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:59.24,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'll continue to support both Mizuki-chan and Hina-san with all my heart!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:02.10,Default,host_meta,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Kotori no Mama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:19.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,In this story, Mizuki's sister comes home from overseas to run a pop-up shop. I felt it was a huge step forward for Mizuki to want the other Niigo members to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:25.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,Kanade and Mafuyu had met Yuuki-san before, but Ena hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:31.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seeing them finally meet was one of the ways the story progressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:38.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,Mizuki loves so many things, like making videos,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:46.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,remaking clothes, visiting boutiques, and looking at makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:57.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,I think it's amazing that they're already facing the question of what they want to do for a career at this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:08.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,When I was looking at colleges, I was just visiting open campuses thinking, "If I'm going to pay for this, I need to study something that leaves me with marketable skills."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:14.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,So I felt like my approach to finding what I liked was completely different from Mizuki's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:23.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Even so, I think it was a very important time for Mizuki to re-examine what they love at their own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:49.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's a big deal to realize that your passion for clothes isn't just a hobby, but something you might want as a career. I was just so happy to see Mizuki smiling.
Comment: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Story Watchalong ===
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:57.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,Alright, so I've picked out some scenes I personally want to talk about. Let's take a look together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:58.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.91,0:24:45.41,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.84,0:24:51.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.80,0:24:53.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.58,0:24:54.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.04,0:24:56.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.52,0:25:04.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,Since I've already chosen my own career path, seeing the moment someone else makes their choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.28,0:25:09.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,even if it's just through an event story,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.10,0:25:14.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,there are definitely moments where you wonder if you're doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.04,0:25:16.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,You definitely have those moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.40,0:25:20.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,But if you can look back 10 or 20 years from now
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.20,0:25:24.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,and feel glad that you made that choice back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.10,0:25:28.98,Default,host,0,0,0,,then I think that's a wonderful thing. And I believe effort is what makes that possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.98,0:25:35.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,When it comes to things that require effort, I don't think there's such a thing as a 'right' or 'wrong' choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.76,0:25:41.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,With a choice that requires effort, maybe in a year or two,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.26,0:25:44.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,you might have times where you regret it and think you shouldn't have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.72,0:25:50.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,But looking back after 10 or 20 years, I'm sure there are times when it all connects in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.48,0:25:53.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,You'll realize, 'If I hadn't done that then, I wouldn't be where I am now.'
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.26,0:25:58.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Even if you're in a different field, I'm sure you'll feel that way. For those of you working hard now,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.00,0:26:11.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,or if there's something you want to strive for, I hope this event story gives you the courage to keep going or make that decision. That's the kind of story it was.
Comment: 0,0:26:12.52,0:26:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Card Illustrations ===
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.52,0:26:16.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, from here, I'd like to talk about the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.72,0:26:18.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll start by reading a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.70,0:26:21.44,Default,host_meta,0,0,0,,This one is from Meshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.44,0:26:23.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.42,0:26:25.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Hello, Sato-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.80,0:26:28.96,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm always having a great time playing ProSeka."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.96,0:26:33.88,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The 4-star illustrations this time, especially Mizuki's, were so good that I went all out on the gacha..."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.88,0:26:34.88,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"...and I managed to get them!"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.88,0:26:39.44,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Just like in 'Secret Distance' or 'Our Escape to the Unknown'..."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.44,0:26:39.94,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"'Michi wa Izuko'..."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.64,0:26:48.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"...the post-trained illustration features Mizuki in a space with a torso."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.28,0:26:52.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,"A torso is like a mannequin for clothes, which often appears in Mizuki's art."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.04,0:26:54.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.70,0:26:56.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.36,0:26:57.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.04,0:26:58.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,This is called a torso.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.20,0:27:01.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,"Reaching out to an unbinding tomorrow... the torso."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.84,0:27:04.70,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's an illustration with Mizuki in a space filled with torsos."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.70,0:27:08.78,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The torso space usually represented Mizuki's dark feelings,"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.78,0:27:13.06,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but this time, they're looking forward after feeling the warmth of family and friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.06,0:27:18.84,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Seeing the space reflect Mizuki's bright and cheerful state of mind,"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.84,0:27:20.42,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I was so happy to see how much their heart has changed."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.42,0:27:25.22,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I can't thank the staff enough for creating such a wonderful scenario,"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.22,0:27:29.26,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and the voice actors for giving the characters such depth and expression."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.26,0:27:32.44,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you for always creating such wonderful events."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.44,0:27:35.12,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Please take care of yourselves and keep up the good work."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.12,0:27:37.78,Default,host_meta,0,0,0,,"I'll be rooting for you as a fellow Toufu," they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.78,0:27:39.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,Meshi, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.96,0:27:47.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,The colors in these illustrations are quite rare for Niigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.68,0:27:51.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,We've had pale colors before, but seeing Niigo bathed in sunlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.84,0:27:54.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,Well, they don't really go outside much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.02,0:28:01.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seeing Niigo during the day is rare, and I felt this specific art style was quite unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.30,0:28:05.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everyone's cards were great, not just Mizuki's, both pre-trained and post-trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.56,0:28:10.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,It makes me realize what amazing artists we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.34,0:28:18.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm really grateful. We also received comments from the illustration team about the outfits,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.46,0:28:21.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,so I'd like to share those as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.28,0:28:24.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,They mentioned that "pure brightness" is quite rare for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.96,0:28:29.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,"The story was inspired by Mizuki, who was accepted by Niigo, wanting to help others who have similar worries..."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.08,0:28:32.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,"...or who can't love themselves, by making clothes for them."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.88,0:28:38.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,"It also draws from the story of Mizuki thinking about their future career in fashion."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.28,0:28:44.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,"To express the image of a future they've finally started to see,"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.50,0:28:48.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,"we chose a simple and pure one-piece design with few elements."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.48,0:28:53.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,"As a highlight, we included the yellow daisy embroidery used in Mizuki's new unit costume..."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.70,0:29:00.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,"...to convey the message of 'being yourself'."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.02,0:29:03.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,"This resulted in a simple outfit design unique to Mizuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.56,0:29:08.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,"To match the song's calm, warm impression and Mizuki's faint hope for the future,"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.40,0:29:15.44,Default,host_meta,0,0,0,,"we used a palette of soft, gentle colors," they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.28,0:29:21.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's true, everyone's cards have a very soft color scheme this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.24,0:29:25.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,And did everyone notice the daisy? Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.00,0:29:26.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,There's a daisy in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.42,0:29:28.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,I see comments about the daisy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.93,0:29:29.43,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.09,0:29:30.67,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.67,0:29:32.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,"The blue traffic light was striking."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.08,0:29:32.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.92,0:29:37.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,Mizuki was born in summer, on August 2... Happy Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.58,0:29:40.18,Default,host,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to say it so casually, but Happy Birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.18,0:29:48.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,Since it's summer, I feel like Mizuki hasn't had many summer-like illustrations until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.64,0:29:54.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,They usually wear long sleeves or clothes that cover their skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.60,0:29:56.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,Though there have been T-shirts and things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.66,0:30:06.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, seeing an illustration that feels like summer the moment you look at it is really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.74,0:30:13.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,With that said, let's take a look at the card illustrations together.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.04,0:30:16.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm on the monitor right now. On everyone's monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.64,0:30:19.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,I believe so, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.12,0:30:23.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,Let's start with Mizuki's pre-trained card.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.97,0:30:24.47,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.28,0:30:28.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,This illustration...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.92,0:30:36.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,Their sister is looking at Mizuki with such a happy smile. In the New Year's event,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.26,0:30:43.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,it really reminds me of Yuuki-san giving a ribbon to a young Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.42,0:30:48.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,And Mizuki's expression while showing her the outfit is just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.60,0:30:50.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,I can't believe this is a pre-trained card.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.48,0:30:52.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.44,0:30:54.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,I love the atmosphere here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.84,0:30:57.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,You can see the torso in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.34,0:30:57.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.90,0:30:59.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,Now, let's look at the post-trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.79,0:31:01.47,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.47,0:31:02.15,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.16,0:31:04.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.72,0:31:12.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,I've always felt that butterflies and ribbons are very symbolic for Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.20,0:31:15.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,Usually, I have this image of Mizuki holding scissors
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.84,0:31:21.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,in their illustrations, but this time, they're in such a bright space.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.26,0:31:29.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,They're hiding their mouth, but you can tell they're definitely smiling, which is so precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.80,0:31:30.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.44,0:31:33.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,Our girl is such a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.52,0:31:35.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,Next up is Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.64,0:31:39.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,And Yuki-san is there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.52,0:31:43.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,I love seeing Ena meet the older sister for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.58,0:31:46.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,and get a bit overwhelmed by how pushy she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.76,0:31:48.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.28,0:31:54.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,If you haven't seen the event story yet, please check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.20,0:31:59.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seeing the sister talk to all of Niigo is a must-see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.00,0:32:03.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Next, isn't this Ena incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.48,0:32:08.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,I think girls with their hair tucked behind their ears are great, and this illustration...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.68,0:32:09.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,is just incredibly good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.48,0:32:11.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,I thought she was a florist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.72,0:32:13.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,Oh, Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.96,0:32:15.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.48,0:32:19.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,Those downcast eyes are great too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.22,0:32:20.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.44,0:32:24.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Next is Len.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.24,0:32:29.82,Default,host,0,0,0,,He's eating the souvenir from the sister, it's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.82,0:32:31.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.92,0:32:32.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,Why is he so cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.36,0:32:36.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Even if that were a protein bar, he'd still be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.00,0:32:38.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,He's just eating the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.28,0:32:38.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.84,0:32:41.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Next, the post-training version.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.12,0:32:43.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Isn't this insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.36,0:32:44.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,I thought it was insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.80,0:32:48.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,I was like, "You're the only one who can pull off short pants like that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.16,0:32:50.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.17,0:32:51.67,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.24,0:32:53.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.60,0:32:57.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,The overall vibe is a rare one for Niigo, which is really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.60,0:33:01.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Is he holding a book about daisies?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.60,0:33:03.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,My knowledge of daisies
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.20,0:33:07.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,is a bit shallow, so I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.04,0:33:08.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,But I bet that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.84,0:33:10.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.72,0:33:13.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,I love the idea of sharing something delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.48,0:33:14.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everything tastes better when you share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.39,0:33:16.89,Default,host,0,0,0,,And this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.32,0:33:18.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.64,0:33:21.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.96,0:33:26.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,These clothes look like something Mizuki, or rather, Yuki-san would pick out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.96,0:33:27.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,This style.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.32,0:33:29.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,She looks a bit troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.76,0:33:31.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,She looks good in them, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.08,0:33:37.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,Setting aside where she'd actually wear it, I wonder if Kanade would really wear this headpiece when she goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.76,0:33:39.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.63,0:33:40.13,Default,host,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.76,0:33:42.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,if it looks good, she should wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.72,0:33:45.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.00,0:33:47.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everyone is always so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.76,0:33:49.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Post-training.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.00,0:33:54.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,She looks like a proper young lady here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.16,0:33:56.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Are these daisies too?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.88,0:33:59.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,The ones on her chest and head.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.27,0:34:00.77,Default,host,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.36,0:34:09.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,In the side story, Kanade is forced to try on all sorts of clothes, and it's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.64,0:34:12.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,Please check out the side story too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.92,0:34:14.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everyone is saying how cute they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.76,0:34:16.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.28,0:34:18.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.52,0:34:22.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,I've realized it's really rare to see Niigo wearing white,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.64,0:34:24.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,after doing all these AfterTalks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.75,0:34:26.25,Default,host,0,0,0,,Mafuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.92,0:34:27.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.64,0:34:29.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.00,0:34:44.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,It might not be a full-on smile, but seeing Mafuyu with a bit more of a smile makes me so happy. This event story really brightened my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.00,0:34:51.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,I think it's wonderful how all the illustrations have this sense of warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.88,0:34:52.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.76,0:34:54.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.80,0:34:57.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, that was the illustration corner. Moving on...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.68,0:35:02.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,For this event, Onuma Parsley-san wrote a new song for us.
Comment: 0,0:35:02.12,0:35:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Song Watchalong ===
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.12,0:35:07.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'd like to watch the MV for "Kazaite" and talk a bit about the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.42,0:35:14.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,But before we watch the 3DMV, I have a comment from the Sega 3DMV production team to share with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.38,0:35:25.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,They said, "In the 3DMV for Kazaite, we used the visual of falling into water to represent Mizuki's wavering emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.02,0:35:30.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,and their inability to be honest with the other members. We used the insert function and spent a lot of time
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.12,0:35:32.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,on the underwater falling sequence through a process of trial and error.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.52,0:35:36.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,While there are still challenges in fully depicting emotional depth,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.22,0:35:40.70,Default,host_meta,0,0,0,,we hope you enjoy this new form of expression through Mizuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.70,0:35:43.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,Alright, let's take a look at the 3DMV right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.58,0:35:44.15,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.00,0:37:56.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Did you see that expression just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.92,0:38:00.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,They're smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.76,0:38:02.98,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.98,0:38:03.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.96,0:38:08.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,I was honestly blown away when I first saw this 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.20,0:38:10.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.92,0:38:13.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,how much the scenery changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.20,0:38:20.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,It goes from a school-like setting to an after-school vibe, with shots through windows showing leaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.44,0:38:25.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,and when they're walking down the hallway, you can see things in the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.36,0:38:29.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,Not Wi-Fi, but... what do you call it? Like dust motes or particles floating in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.76,0:38:31.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,The direction is so detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.88,0:38:33.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,I was wondering how they even did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.52,0:38:36.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,It was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.22,0:38:41.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,The way the camera circles around and the characters swap out...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.62,0:38:45.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,The production value was so high, it really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.16,0:38:47.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,It was just so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.80,0:38:49.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad we could look back on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.44,0:38:54.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,The 2DMV is also incredible, I've watched it so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.78,0:38:59.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,Regarding the 2DMV, this is just my personal take,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.06,0:39:02.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,since nothing has been explicitly stated and I haven't heard the details yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.28,0:39:06.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,but the 2DMV has a setting that looks like a birthday party, with a seat of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.26,0:39:12.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,Mizuki is there by a cake, and the camera pans over things that symbolize what Mizuki is "adorning" themselves with.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.08,0:39:16.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,Like the letter from their older sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.14,0:39:21.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,and ribbons... seeing those things in the 2D version was really wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.92,0:39:24.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Both versions were amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.04,0:39:25.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,The sheer amount of information in them is staggering.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.92,0:39:35.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,As for the song, I felt that Mizuki's previous songs often had a lot of painful lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.58,0:39:46.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to compare it to past songs, but I really felt this one has a lot of forward-looking lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.40,0:39:51.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,Even so, it still captures those wavering emotions inside Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.44,0:39:57.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,I don't think Mizuki is someone who can just let everything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.44,0:40:02.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,So I consulted with the director about the nuances, like how much
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.50,0:40:09.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,strength to add or subtract. We talked a lot while creating this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.54,0:40:15.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,There are parts where the audio sounds like a radio, and I asked,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.96,0:40:20.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,"Instead of just putting the emotion out there, can I try making my voice sound a bit raspy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.88,0:40:26.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,We discussed a lot of those subtle nuances during the recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.30,0:40:35.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,I hope you'll enjoy both the full 2DMV and the 3DMV where Mizuki smiles at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.10,0:40:38.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Both are already uploaded to the official ProSeka YouTube channel,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.88,0:40:41.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,so please go check them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.52,0:40:51.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,And with that, our short time together is coming to an end. This concludes the ProSeka AfterTalk for the "Reaching Out for an Unbreakable Tomorrow" edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.58,0:40:54.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,To everyone watching the stream, how did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.00,0:40:55.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,Let's take a quick look at the comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.75,0:40:57.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.34,0:41:01.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,Someone said, "Onuma Parsley's MV and the Niigo 2D version have different vibes, and both are great."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.38,0:41:02.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's so true.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.24,0:41:05.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,For Mizuki... how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.08,0:41:12.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Students thinking about their future... and ProSeka is also approaching its 5th anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.00,0:41:17.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,Mizuki has been through a lot leading up to this 5th anniversary, and in the midst of that, they're looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.20,0:41:20.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,It shows that while things happened, they're still thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.70,0:41:24.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,"I'm going to do my best!" I think "Kazaite" depicts those Niigo-like feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.32,0:41:28.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,But in Onuma-san's version,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.60,0:41:29.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,how do I describe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.60,0:41:36.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's like a working adult who's tired, but still trying to encourage themselves to keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.94,0:41:42.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,I felt that depending on the singer and the way it's expressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.96,0:41:49.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,the song itself has a huge range.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.16,0:41:54.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really felt that with "Kazaite." Please check out Onuma-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.68,0:41:55.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,Is it called a 2D version? What would you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.92,0:41:56.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,How should I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.50,0:41:57.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,The original MV?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.90,0:42:02.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,I hope you'll enjoy that MV as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.42,0:42:14.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,Looking back, a lot of Niigo stories have been quite heavy or felt a bit suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.52,0:42:23.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,But this time, I think it's a story that high schoolers
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.36,0:42:35.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,can really relate to on a personal level. It's a very down-to-earth event story.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.72,0:42:39.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,Things like deciding on a career path,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.36,0:42:47.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,lacking the confidence to acknowledge what you like, or not being able to love the things you love...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.40,0:42:52.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,If there's anyone feeling that way right now, whether you're a student or a working adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.70,0:42:57.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,and you haven't seen the event story or heard the song yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.32,0:43:05.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,I think there are words in this story and song that will really resonate with you because of who you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.12,0:43:12.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,I hope everyone, both adults and students, will enjoy it to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.44,0:43:20.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, for those who haven't finished the story for "Reaching Out for an Unbreakable Tomorrow" yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.02,0:43:24.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,even after the next event starts, you can still read the whole story from the archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.76,0:43:25.86,Default,host,0,0,0,,Please give it a read.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.86,0:43:30.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,This will probably be uploaded to YouTube at a later date,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.14,0:43:32.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,so it's perfectly fine to wait for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.28,0:43:35.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,We're always looking for your messages here at AfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.62,0:43:43.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,You can submit them through the official ProSeka Discord channel or via email.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.72,0:43:47.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,Once the next event starts, please be sure to send yours in!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.84,0:43:51.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Just make sure your messages are related to the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.68,0:43:55.86,Default,host,0,0,0,,August is almost over, and once September is through,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.86,0:43:59.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,the Anniversary Festival will be waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.02,0:44:04.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,We've been busy preparing for it, so please look forward to that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.64,0:44:10.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'd be so happy if you did. August is ending, but the heat is here to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.88,0:44:15.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, please be careful of heatstroke. If you feel like it's too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.00,0:44:18.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,please don't hesitate to get away from the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.56,0:44:20.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,Keeping cool is the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.46,0:44:23.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,I hope we can all see each other at the Anniversary Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.76,0:44:25.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting for you, whether on the stream or at the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.94,0:44:28.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you all for watching until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.50,0:44:32.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,Let's all survive this summer together. See you all again soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.44,0:44:34.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.50,0:44:35.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Bye!
